Uncertain dynamic response of mid-latitude winter precipitation
                    Lei Gu 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0001-8291-98941,2, Dominik L. Schumacher 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0003-2699-28801, Sebastian Sippel 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0002-4510-44583, Erich M. Fischer 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0003-1931-67371, Istvan Dunkl3, Robin Noyelle1, Jitendra Singh 
